{"id":"plugins/ngrid-bootstrap/pagination","title":"Pagination","contents":"<h1 id=\"pagination\"><a href=\"#pagination\" aria-hidden><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Pagination</h1>\n<p>Pagination UI controls for <strong>nGrid</strong> using bootstrap pagination UI via the <a href=\"https://ng-bootstrap.github.io/#/components/pagination/overview\">NgbPaginationModule</a> module from <strong>ng-bootstrap</strong>.</p>\n<blockquote class=\"info icon\">\n<div class=\"icon-location\"></div>\n If you're not familiar with pagination and the logical implementation please take a minute and read about \n<a href=\"../../../concepts/datasource/triggers/pagination\">pagination</a>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"synchronousclient-side-pagination\"><a href=\"#synchronousclient-side-pagination\" aria-hidden><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Synchronous/Client-Side Pagination</h2>\n<div pbl-example-view=\"pbl-bs-pagination-example\" containerClass=\"pbl-docs-bootstrap\"></div>\n<h3 id=\"asynchronous-page-number-based\"><a href=\"#asynchronous-page-number-based\" aria-hidden><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Asynchronous: Page Number based</h3>\n<div pbl-example-view=\"pbl-bs-async-page-number-example\" containerClass=\"pbl-docs-bootstrap\"></div>\n"}